item.title: Boys Over Flowers Session 1 Episode 1
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Jan-di is an average high school girl whose parents operate a Laundromat. One day she delivers laundry to Shin-hwa high school, where the top 1% of the wealthy children gets to go, and accidentally saves a student from a suicidal attempt. After this incident, she is scouted to this prestigious school as a swimming athlete.

item.title: Boys Over Flowers Session 1 Episode 2
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Jandi gets Jihoo’s help when students attack her at the locker room. Jandi, cannot stand Junpyo’s smugness, goes to see Junpyo and kicks him right in the face. Rather than paying her back, Junpyo finds his curiosity from this girl who reminds him of his older sister, Junhee. After school finishes, unknown guards kidnap Jandi. She wakes up and notices the unbelievable things that are happening right in front of her eyes…

item.title: Casey Affleck on Being Learning to Love Awards Season
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
In many cases, the performances — particularly Affleck’s — started with questions. “Casey is great to work with, because he’s very demanding about all the right things,” Lonergan said of his leading man. “
He really wants to know specifically why something is happening, when it’s happening, why something else isn’t happening, why his manner is like this with one person but not another person. Exploring all those subtleties and specifics with an actor is really fun. Plus we like to yell at each other.”

item.title: Steven Soderberghs Logan lucky lands bleecker street
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Bleecker Street announced it has partnered with Fingerprint Releasing to distribute Steven Soderbergh’s comedy “Logan Lucky.”
Featuring an all-star cast, including Channing Tatum, Adam Driver, Riley Keough, Hilary Swank, Seth MacFarlane, Katie Holmes, and Daniel Craig, “Logan Lucky” follows two brothers who attempt to pull off a heist during a NASCAR race.

item.title: When Does the Next ‘Star Wars’ Movie Come Out?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Since Disney purchased LucasFilm, “Star Wars” fans have suddenly been flush with new stories.
The galaxy far, far away has new cartoons, books, comics and movies to flesh it out. But now that there’s a new “Star Wars” due every year, there’s an eternal question: When does the next “Star Wars” movie come out?

item.title: Oscars: Amy Adams, Dwayne Johnson Join New Crop of Presenters
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Other newly-named presenters include Riz Ahmed, Javier Bardem, John Cho, Felicity Jones, Leslie Mann, Janelle Monáe, David Oyelowo and Charlize Theron.
“No matter who you are or where you live, movies bring us together,” De Luca and Todd said in a joint statement. “Through indelible, fearless performances these extraordinary actors help make it happen. We are thrilled to welcome them to the 89th Oscars stage.”

item.title: Lion
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: A five-year-old Indian boy gets lost on the streets of Calcutta, thousands of kilometers from home. He survives many challenges before being adopted by a couple in Australia; 25 years later, he sets out to find his lost family.

item.title: The Girl on the Train
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Rachel Watson, devastated by her recent divorce, spends her daily commute fantasizing about the seemingly perfect couple who live in a house that her train passes every day, until one morning she sees something shocking happen there and becomes entangled in the mystery that unfolds.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: What you see can hurt you.

item.title: Jack Reacher: Never Go Back
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Jack Reacher must uncover the truth behind a major government conspiracy in order to clear his name. On the run as a fugitive from the law, Reacher uncovers a potential secret from his past that could change his life forever.

item.title: Room
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Jack is a young boy of 5 years old who has lived all his life in one room. He believes everything within it are the only real things in the world. But what will happen when his Ma suddenly tells him that there are other things outside of Room?

item.title: Avatar
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: In the 22nd century, a paraplegic Marine is dispatched to the moon Pandora on a unique mission, but becomes torn between following orders and protecting an alien civilization.

item.title: Star Wars: The Force Awakens
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Thirty years after defeating the Galactic Empire, Han Solo and his allies face a new threat from the evil Kylo Ren and his army of Stormtroopers.

item.title: The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Immediately after the events of The Desolation of Smaug, Bilbo and the dwarves try to defend Erebor's mountain of treasure from others who claim it: the men of the ruined Laketown and the elves of Mirkwood. Meanwhile an army of Orcs led by Azog the Defiler is marching on Erebor, fueled by the rise of the dark lord Sauron. Dwarves, elves and men must unite, and the hope for Middle-Earth falls into Bilbo's hands.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies
Witness the defining chapter of the Middle-Earth saga

item.title: The Shawshank Redemption
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Framed in the 1940s for the double murder of his wife and her lover, upstanding banker Andy Dufresne begins a new life at the Shawshank prison, where he puts his accounting skills to work for an amoral warden. During his long stretch in prison, Dufresne comes to be admired by the other inmates -- including an older prisoner named Red -- for his integrity and unquenchable sense of hope.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Fear can hold you prisoner. Hope can set you free.

item.title: Boys Over Flowers
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: A working class girl winds up at an exclusive prep school. Unassuming high school girl Jan Di stands up to -- and eventually falls for -- a spoiled rich kid who belongs to the school's most powerfu clique.

item.title: Captain America: Civil War
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Following the events of Age of Ultron, the collective governments of the world pass an act designed to regulate all superhuman activity. This polarizes opinion amongst the Avengers, causing two factions to side with Iron Man or Captain America, which causes an epic battle between former allies.

item.title: Miss Peregrine's Home for Peculiar Children
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: A teenager finds himself transported to an island where he must help protect a group of orphans with special powers from creatures intent on destroying them.

item.title: Jurassic World
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Twenty-two years after the events of Jurassic Park, Isla Nublar now features a fully functioning dinosaur theme park, Jurassic World, as originally envisioned by John Hammond.

item.title: Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: In 1926, Newt Scamander arrives at the Magical Congress of the United States of America with a magically expanded briefcase, which houses a number of dangerous creatures and their habitats. When the creatures escape from the briefcase, it sends the American wizarding authorities after Newt, and threatens to strain even further the state of magical and non-magical relations.

item.title: John Wick
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: After the sudden death of his beloved wife, John Wick receives one last gift from her, a beagle puppy named Daisy, and a note imploring him not to forget how to love. But John's mourning is interrupted when his 1969 Boss Mustang catches the eye of sadistic thug Iosef Tarasov who breaks into his house and steals it, beating John unconscious in the process. Unwittingly, he has just reawakened one of the most brutal assassins the underworld has ever known.

item.title: Arrival
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Taking place after alien crafts land around the world, an expert linguist is recruited by the military to determine whether they come in peace or are a threat.

item.title: Passengers

item.content:encoded: A spacecraft traveling to a distant colony planet and transporting thousands of people has a malfunction in its sleep chambers. As a result, two passengers are awakened 90 years early.

item.title: Arrow
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Spoiled billionaire playboy Oliver Queen is missing and presumed dead when his yacht is lost at sea. He returns five years later a changed man, determined to clean up the city as a hooded vigilante armed with a bow.

item.title: Hacksaw Ridge
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: WWII American Army Medic Desmond T. Doss, who served during the Battle of Okinawa, refuses to kill people and becomes the first Conscientious Objector in American history to win the Congressional Medal of Honor.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: One of the greatest heroes in American history never fired a bullet.
